---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const jsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Our Research Methodology",
  "description": "How CreditDoc evaluates and rates credit repair companies, personal lenders, and financial services.",
  "url": "https://creditdoc.co/methodology/"
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Research Methodology | How We Rate Credit Repair Companies - CreditDoc"
  description="Learn how CreditDoc evaluates credit repair companies and financial services using our 5-factor rating system, including data sources, review process, and independence standards."
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-border">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-light px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">Methodology</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-text sm:text-5xl">Our Research Methodology</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Every review and rating on CreditDoc follows a rigorous, repeatable research process. Here's exactly how we evaluate the companies featured on our site.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="space-y-16">

      <!-- 5-Factor Rating System -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Our 5-Factor Rating System</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Every company listed on CreditDoc is evaluated across five core factors. Each factor is scored on a scale of 1.0 to 5.0, and the overall rating is an equally weighted average of all five scores.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-white font-bold text-sm">1</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">Value</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
                  Is the service worth the price? We evaluate monthly fees, setup costs, money-back guarantees, and the overall cost-to-benefit ratio. We compare pricing against the breadth and quality of services offered, and consider whether lower-priced alternatives deliver comparable results.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-white font-bold text-sm">2</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">Effectiveness</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
                  Does the company deliver results? We analyze publicly available outcomes data, user-reported score improvements, CFPB complaint volumes relative to company size, and the range of dispute strategies employed (goodwill letters, debt validation, cease-and-desist letters, etc.).
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-white font-bold text-sm">3</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">Customer Service</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
                  How responsive and helpful is the company? We evaluate availability of support channels (phone, email, chat), whether clients are assigned a dedicated advisor, response times based on user reports, and overall customer satisfaction as reflected in third-party reviews.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-white font-bold text-sm">4</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">Transparency</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
                  Is the company upfront about pricing, processes, and realistic expectations? We evaluate whether pricing is clearly displayed on the website, whether the company makes unrealistic promises (such as guaranteeing specific score increases), and the clarity of their contracts and terms of service.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-white font-bold text-sm">5</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">Ease of Use</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
                  How easy is it to get started and stay informed? We evaluate the sign-up process, whether the company offers a mobile app or online portal, the quality of progress tracking tools, and overall user experience based on public reviews.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Data Sources -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Our Data Sources</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We cross-reference multiple independent data sources to form a comprehensive picture of each company. No single source determines our rating.
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-2">Better Business Bureau (BBB)</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">Accreditation status, letter grades, complaint history, and resolution track record.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-2">CFPB Complaint Database</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">Consumer complaints filed with the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau, including company responses.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-2">User Reviews</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">Verified customer reviews from Trustpilot, Google, BBB, and other platforms, analyzed for common themes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-2">Direct Company Research</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">We visit company websites directly to verify pricing, features, service tiers, and terms of service.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-2">Pricing Verification</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">Monthly checks of all listed prices against current company websites to ensure accuracy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-2">Regulatory Records</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">State attorney general actions, FTC enforcement actions, and court records when available.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review Process -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Our Review Process</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Each company listing goes through a structured review pipeline before publication. Here's how it works:
        </p>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute left-[19px] top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-border sm:left-[23px]"></div>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="relative flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 z-10 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-sm font-bold sm:h-12 sm:w-12">1</div>
              <div class="pt-1 sm:pt-2">
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text">Initial Research</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">We identify the company and gather baseline information: founding date, headquarters, services offered, target market, and key differentiators.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 z-10 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-sm font-bold sm:h-12 sm:w-12">2</div>
              <div class="pt-1 sm:pt-2">
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text">Data Collection</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">We pull data from all sources listed above: BBB, CFPB, user reviews, direct pricing verification, and regulatory records.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 z-10 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-sm font-bold sm:h-12 sm:w-12">3</div>
              <div class="pt-1 sm:pt-2">
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text">Expert Analysis</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Our team applies the 5-factor rating system, writes the detailed review narrative, identifies pros/cons, and determines "best for" categories.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 z-10 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-sm font-bold sm:h-12 sm:w-12">4</div>
              <div class="pt-1 sm:pt-2">
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text">Peer Review</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Ratings and review content are cross-checked for accuracy, consistency with our methodology, and fairness.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 z-10 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-sm font-bold sm:h-12 sm:w-12">5</div>
              <div class="pt-1 sm:pt-2">
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text">Publication</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">The review is published on CreditDoc with a "last updated" date. All reviews include our editorial diagnosis -- a plain-language summary of who the service is best for and what to watch out for.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 z-10 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-sm font-bold sm:h-12 sm:w-12">6</div>
              <div class="pt-1 sm:pt-2">
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text">Ongoing Monitoring</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">All listings are reviewed quarterly. Pricing is verified monthly. If a company's BBB rating changes, receives regulatory action, or makes significant changes to their services, we update our review accordingly.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Update Frequency -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Update Frequency</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white overflow-hidden">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-bg-alt">
                <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-text">What We Check</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-text">Frequency</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-border">
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">Pricing and service tiers</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">Monthly</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">Full review and ratings</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">Quarterly</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">BBB ratings and accreditation</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">Quarterly</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">CFPB complaint data</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">Quarterly</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">Regulatory actions or legal issues</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">As they occur</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">Company closures or acquisitions</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-3 text-muted">As they occur</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Editorial Independence -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Editorial Independence</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary-light/30 p-6 sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-sm text-text leading-relaxed mb-4">
            CreditDoc earns revenue through affiliate partnerships with some of the companies listed on our site. When you click certain links and sign up for a service, we may receive a referral fee. This is how we fund our research and keep the site free for consumers.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong>However, compensation never influences our editorial content.</strong> Our ratings, rankings, and recommendations are determined solely by our research methodology described above. We frequently feature and recommend companies that do not have an affiliate relationship with us.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text leading-relaxed">
            If you believe any of our reviews contain inaccurate information, we encourage you to contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@creditdoc.co" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@creditdoc.co</a>. We take corrections seriously and will investigate promptly. For our full affiliate disclosure, visit our <a href="/disclosure/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Disclosure page</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Rating Scale -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Rating Scale</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-positive-light text-positive font-bold text-lg">5.0</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text">Outstanding</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted">Exceptional across all five evaluation criteria. Industry-leading in multiple areas.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-positive-light text-positive font-bold text-lg">4.0</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text">Excellent</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted">Strong performance overall with minor areas for improvement. Recommended.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-warning-light text-warning font-bold text-lg">3.0</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text">Good</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted">Solid service with notable strengths and weaknesses. Worth considering depending on your priorities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-warning-light text-warning font-bold text-lg">2.0</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text">Below Average</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted">Significant concerns in one or more areas. Proceed with caution and consider alternatives.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-negative-light text-negative font-bold text-lg">1.0</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text">Poor</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted">Serious issues identified. Significant red flags, regulatory concerns, or consistent negative consumer reports.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Suggest a Correction -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Suggest a Correction</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We strive for accuracy in everything we publish, but we're not infallible. If you notice incorrect pricing, outdated information, a factual error, or believe a rating doesn't reflect the current state of a company, please let us know.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@creditdoc.co" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@creditdoc.co</a> with the subject line "Correction Request" and include:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 ml-4 list-disc text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed space-y-1">
            <li>The page URL or company name</li>
            <li>What information you believe is incorrect</li>
            <li>The correct information (with a source, if possible)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We review all correction requests within 5 business days and will update our content if warranted.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
